title: Womb Baseball
description: Katie and Ashley learn a little bit more about Travis (00:55) and then get into Lionel Messi and how he still uses a fax machine (24:23). Chris Webber talked about Smurfs, LeBron found a meme about his hair funny & Dianna Taurasi isn’t happy with an official (1:00:50). How old is too old to be superstitious with your teams (1:07:24) and when defending a client goes too far (1:12:16). Finally, Dan Snyder is on Twitter and Katie has one simple request (1:46:15).
itunes:author: ESPN, Katie Nolan
itunes:subtitle: Katie and Ashley break down all of the MOST pressing sports stories?
